number_of_reviews <- nyc_airbnb %>%
  group_by(room_type) %>%
  summarise(mean_price = median(price), na.rm = TRUE) %>%
  pivot_wider(
    names_from = room_type,
    values_from = mean_price
  )

repeat_hosts = nyc_airbnb %>%
  group_by(host_id) %>%
  summarize(listing_count = n()) %>%
  filter(listing_count > 1)
